txt.en: Céolstan stands in the stables of Harwick.\n\nYou should bring the relics to Céolstan.
The draugar of Dwolung Hole bear relics upon them that may be of interest to the people of Harwick.

'Hm, I do not recognize the symbols on the relics you collected from the draugar. They almost look to be of a Dunlending quality, but I cannot tell for sure. Perhaps that tomb was from before the time of the Rohirrim.\n\n'I will see that these get put in better hands than mine, for I am useless in such matters, but thank you for bringing them to me.'
The draugar of Dwolung Hole bear relics upon them that may be of interest to the people of Harwick.
Draugar can be found in Dwolung Hole in the Wold.\n\nYou should defeat draugar and collect the relics they carry.
